description._content: [Fishmarket and bourse (i.e. weighing house), Amsterdam, Holland] [between ca. 1890 and ca. 1900]. 1 photomechanical print : photochrom, color. Notes: Photo shows De Waag or weighing house at right, originally a gate in the city walls and now a subway station, Nieuwmarkt. (Source: Flickr Commons project and Wikipedia, 2009) Title from the Detroit Publishing Co., catalogue J, foreign section. Detroit, Mich. : Detroit Publishing Company, c1905. Print no. "8465".
